name: Set.mul_zero_subset
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝ : MulZeroClass α
s : Set α
⊢ HasSubset.Subset (HMul.hMul s 0) 0
decl: lemma mul_zero_subset (s : Set α) : s * 0 ⊆ 0 := by simp [subset_def, mem_mul]

name: Set.zero_mul_subset
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝ : MulZeroClass α
s : Set α
⊢ HasSubset.Subset (HMul.hMul 0 s) 0

name: Set.Nonempty.mul_zero
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝ : MulZeroClass α
s : Set α
hs : s.Nonempty
⊢ Eq (HMul.hMul s 0) 0
decl:
lemma Nonempty.mul_zero (hs : s.Nonempty) : s * 0 = 0 :=
  s.mul_zero_subset.antisymm <| by simpa [mem_mul] using hs
